This paper deals with transmission strategies for a cloud radio access network, which involves the use of digital fronthaul or backhaul links. This topic is closely related to network infrastructure (cs.NI), information theory (cs.IT), control systems (cs.SY), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
